async with get_temp_empty_database() as temp_empty_database:
    await temp_empty_database.insert_all(ExchangeDataTables.OHLCV, symbol=[
        'xyz', 'abc'], timestamp=[1, 2], price=[1, 10], date=['01', '05'])
    assert await temp_empty_database.select(ExchangeDataTables.OHLCV) == [(
        2, 'abc', '10', '05'), (1, 'xyz', '1', '01')]
    assert await temp_empty_database.select(ExchangeDataTables.OHLCV, date='05'
        ) == [(2, 'abc', '10', '05')]
